diagram:
flowchart TD
  Start[What are you integrating?] --> Sync{Need immediate request response?}
  Sync -->|Yes| APIM[API Management front APIs]
  Sync -->|No| Required{Must one handler perform work?}
  Required -->|Yes simple backlog| Storage[Storage Queue]
  Required -->|Yes enterprise command| SBQ[Service Bus Queue]
  Required -->|No fact happened| Many{Who needs it?}
  Many -->|Multiple durable subscribers| SBT[Service Bus Topic]
  Many -->|Reactive handlers| EG[Event Grid]
  Many -->|High volume time series| EH[Event Hubs]
  Start --> Procedure{Mostly a business procedure?}
  Procedure -->|Yes| LA[Logic Apps workflow]
